DOC.brief_summary: The purpose of this study is to compare human embryo in vitro development in sequential and single-step culture medium using time-lapse imaging.
DOC.brief_title: Comparison of Human Embryo Development Using Sequential and Single Media With Time-lapse Imaging
DOC.criteria: 6 or more normal embryos following egg retrieval and fertilization. Female patients aged 2140 years or 2155 years who are using an egg donor. Patients using fresh or frozen ejaculated sperm Previous history of cancer Day 3 embryo transfer
